ElementDef.EDComments: Used to determine where multiple-volume Bills should be divided into separate books. Splitting can occur anywhere within the Part/Chapter/CrossHeading structure of the clauses, or between Schedules. A split will never occur within a Schedule. Typically the split is only required for long Bills (e.g. Fincance Bill) where there is a physical limit to the number of pages that can be stapled by the printer. Mekon\qs FDK plugin actually allows for multiple splits, however, this will never really be more than 2 volumes.
